                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc type="RecordTransaction">
                              <locus target="#54v" facs="057"/> Record of purchase of land, date unclear</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <desc type="Asmat">
                              <locus target="#56r #56v" facs="058 059"/>
                          Prayer of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ መስቀል፡</foreign> for salvation with
                          the asmat found in the <title ref="LIT1295Dersan"/>
                          and the Hebrew letters found in Ps 118
                        </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">Note of ownership by <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ መስቀል፡</foreign> and his wife <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወለተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign>, <locus target="#56r" facs="058"> f. 56r and passim</locus></desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <desc>
                          Overlooked words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#ir(ecto) #7v #10v #18r #44r #50r" facs="001 010 013 020 046 052"/>, etc.);
                          and overlooked lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#1r #69r" facs="003 071"/>);
                          and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#5r" facs="007"> f. 5r, line 19</locus> and <locus target="#15r" facs="017"> f. 15r, line 2</locus>)
                        </desc>
                        </item>
